    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-02-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-02-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="370"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d370">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Unofficial.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Romero</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-02-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 1, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>MY <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Sir:</hi> Having sent yesterday a telegraphic
                    despatch to the Mexican consul at San Francisco, California, asking for reliable
                    information on the reported execution of Mr. Carman and bombardment of Mazatlan,
                    I have just received an answer denying those rumors. I enclose to you for your
                    information a copy of that answer.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, very truly, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>M. ROMERO.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
                <pb facs="0594" n="524" xml:id="pg_524"/>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">[San Francisco, California, dated
                        1st.—Received February 1, 1867—1.50 p. m.]</note>
                    <head>
                        <persName type="from">Mr. Godoy</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                            Romero</persName>
                    </head>
                    <p>Señor Don <hi rend="smallcaps">Matias Romero,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Mexican Minister:</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>The news false. I have letters from Mazatlan of January 29.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>J. A. GODOY.</signed>
                    </closer>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
